      "title" : "The day you let Broadway and R&B take the birthday spotlight",
      "description" : "The night began with a quiet mix—keshi, Ariana Grande, and Laufey—before a full run through “Hamilton” took over, from “Say No to This” to “The World Was Wide Enough.” By morning, The Weeknd and Kali Uchis circled back, and late evening closed with a spin of “Golden” and “Lose My Mind.” 338 minutes, 114 tracks, 109 artists—your birthday, scored in Broadway and R&B.",
