      "title" : "The day you let 2000s club anthems crash your afternoon",
      "description" : "The morning pulsed with “Stereo Love” and K-pop OSTs, but by afternoon, you rewound to a golden era: Black Eyed Peas, Rihanna, and Nicki Minaj powered a “clubbing like it's the 2000's” set, with “Fire Burning” and “Kiss Me Thru The Phone” making cameo appearances. 287 minutes, 101 tracks, 85 artists—your most nostalgic day, with a 2000s dancefloor at its heart.",
