      "reason" : "BIGGEST_TOP_ARTIST_DAY",
      "title" : "The day you let Don Toliver headline your all-day festival",
      "description" : "From a late-night “FIELD TRIP” to a full afternoon and evening with Don Toliver—“Love Sick” to “HARDSTONE PSYCHO”—your day was a showcase of your top artist. Kendrick Lamar, SZA, and Travis Scott made cameos, but Toliver ruled the queue. 221 minutes, 73 tracks, 53 artists—your most Don Toliver–dedicated day of the year.",
