      "description" : "You opened the night with a parade of Disney anthems, from “Love Is an Open Door” to “A Whole New World,” then let Belle’s soundtrack soundtrack your afternoon in endless loops. Don Toliver and Travis Scott brought a sharp turn to the evening, before the day closed on a high note of repeats and genre shifts. 523 minutes, 175 tracks, 148 artists—your most epic listening marathon of the year.",
